data.description: 6-Acre Private Oasis Designed for Luxury-Living for Owners and Their Show Dogs!  This amazing property includes a modern and beautifully updated 2100 Sq. Ft. home and there's an adjoining 2000 sq ft climate-controlled dog kennel facility w/ 8 indoor/outdoor dog runs, full bath plus a wash station for your pups, office space & garage area w/ overhead door. Property was originally designed to raise show-dogs and no expense was spared. Enclosed Indoor/Outdoor cattery for your feline friends completes the farm.  6 ft chain link fence around the half-acre back yard where the pool and gorgeous wooden pergola are located.  Like new composite decking connects the pool to a covered patio area. Like new automatic Generac Generator is included and will keep the power on in the house and the kennel in the event of power outages. Many upgrades on this well-maintained home that's 15 minutes from Camdenton. Kennel facility could have many options and uses, it's a very nice building, make it yours!
